code: Inductive sublistT {A: Type}: list A -> list A -> Type := | sublistT_nil_nil: sublistT nil nil | sublistT_cons: forall a {l1 l2}, sublistT l1 l2 -> sublistT l1 (a :: l2) | sublistT_cons_cons: forall a {l1 l2}, sublistT l1 l2 -> sublistT (a :: l1) (a :: l2).
Definition sublistT_refl {A: Type}: forall (l: list A), sublistT l l := fix sublistT_refl l := match l with | nil => sublistT_nil_nil | a :: l' => sublistT_cons_cons a (sublistT_refl l') end.
